topic.title: Place to share STL files?
topic.body: Does anyone know of a place on ZeroNet where we can share STL files for 3d printing? I'm thinking of something like thingiverse or grabcad.

1565203721_1MprJ7cBPUTpDquydwCvZGQAbGos8.body:
> [styromaniac](#comment_882_16NS3rBdW9zpLmLSQoD8nLTtNVsRFtVBhd): None exclusively for STL, but the following is a good one: http://127.0.0.1:43110/1CiXRY9ATZSoZqBzwMfXEMsKtPRt2aQoF2/ [...]

Very cool! Thanks for being so helpful.
